First Department,

March, 1938.

(March 4, 1938.) Edward H. Ryan and New York & Staten Island Land Company, Appellants, v. Marie P. Driscoll, Individually, and as Executrix, etc., of Michael E. Driscoll, Deceased, Respondent.

Judgment unanimously affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
